				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%A1p/C%E1%BA%A7n-Ch%C3%ADnh-l%C3%A2u-ph%C3%BA/poem-FTw3BG-GzcqAD0laK1NgHw">Cần Chính lâu phú - 勤政樓賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%A1p/author-3lsm43EvROLW2MsmzDXkTg">Nguyễn Pháp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/H%C3%A1n-V%C4%83n-%C4%90%E1%BA%BF/poem-Wi_kzq_-dtQp6qTSnUNXYA">Hán Văn Đế - 漢文帝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Anh-T%C3%B4ng/author-YFBCcaKGsPA7uILcS-B8_Q">Trần Anh Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Khi%C3%AAn-Ng%C6%B0u-Ch%E1%BB%A9c-N%E1%BB%AF/poem-R0E5HQ8ZXx7Zfo7w0B1qwA">Khiên Ngưu, Chức Nữ - 牽牛織女</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Trung/Kinh-hoa/poem-jvJ1YC7zhj21ffj9r21DaA">Kinh hoa - 經花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Trung/author-WOCgNZ_93pZdcSkZIzjU7A">Lý Trung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Long-An-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-Ch%C3%ADnh/poem-I1MpxlEvOJ_fscIJzTd6Lg">Long An – Đồng Chính - 隆安同正</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/Mai/poem-IQzokI9Lthh6LNIFHp-jkA">Mai - 梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/Minh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-gia-hu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-3aa2tlihTrwlAHWnLopSow">Minh Đạo gia huấn - 明道家訓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%